{"tid":1970732,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今次泰中大戰之後,相信唔少香港人都想提升幽默感,想學嘢既就入嚟","createTime":"2020-04-13T11:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T14:13:30.000Z","uid":157510,"like":17,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"914f50e8f95d095fff41bb5f8ef388f167322b78","tid":1970732,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"小弟自問睇咗陶傑先生既作品都好多年<br />\n唔多唔少都學到佢嗰種高質素既英式幽默<br />\n見到咁多連登仔睇泰仔整既meme笑到碌地<br />\n我亦都唔介意露兩手俾大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下就係我既一個經歷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =對方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我屌你老母!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知道你頭先食咗D乜嘢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(大家一定估我會係答佢屎,但我係文明人,英式既幽默係唔會咁粗呸)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我食咩關你撚事呀?     </span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(其實我之前嗰番說話既用意係挖個氹俾佢踩,好明顯,佢已經上釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你頭先食咗<span style=\"color: violet;\">蕃薯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你UP乜柒呀?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(依個時候<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑點</span></span>就嚟喇,大家注意！！！)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為你用緊把口放屁呀,哈哈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個對話同我預判到既一句都冇差<br />\n但係要去到我既境界最緊要都係多學多睇多寫<br />\n要做個木獨仔定幽默仔就要睇你努力喇<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"8a07e471d1bfb57b790bbb6afeae57042e0ed88b","tid":1970732,"uid":15605,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"002049071240eafd0723fc87cf4d13389b1f2a5b","tid":1970732,"uid":76747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"..........."},{"pid":"ab87ac48082c08842ed916dae43ccb39928c0f5d","tid":1970732,"uid":205339,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴？"},{"pid":"86c401ebf5c754fd90f4af73396cab9f0576ba63","tid":1970732,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a07e471d1bfb57b790bbb6afeae57042e0ed88b","tid":1970732,"uid":15605,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"你都睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f2ad6dbd0efd8e17cd1e750d098d7191a1765f","tid":1970732,"uid":205339,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"ab87ac48082c08842ed916dae43ccb39928c0f5d","tid":1970732,"uid":205339,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"羅馬式幽默<br />\n因為條條大路通羅馬<br />\n但我就話條條大路通陰間"},{"pid":"5109e1